import { Card, CardActionArea, CardActions, CardContent, CardMedia, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import React from 'react'

export const Feed = () => {
  return (
    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
      <CardActionArea>
        <CardMedia
          component="img"
          height="140"
          image="https://www.trendyol.com/magaza/teknosa-m-107870?sk=1"
          alt="teknosa"
        />
        <CardContent>
          <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
            teknosa
          </Typography>
          
        </CardContent>
      </CardActionArea>
      <CardActions>
        <Button backgrounColor="orange" size="small" color="inherit">
         alışverişe başla
        </Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
  );
}
